column5: Hi everyone,  I am relatively new to this board, although have been reading it while not actively posting.  I thought that I would post a few pictures of the Walleye that we have been catching here on the Bay of Quinte so far this 2007-2008 Harwater season.  Jeff Quinte Ice Fishing Team
Nice mess of fish they will make for a good fish fry  rob
some nice Gold ya got there... Thanks for sharing!
wow the perch have seen to grown into a nice size over the last few years. Maybe a perch destination other then Sicoe in the future. Thanks for sharing!
Very nice!...thanks for posting the report
Thats some very impressive walleyes you guys caught !!!!.  ..nice pics too    cheers
